<span id="freeTextContainer3899360781164996949"><strong>Good story,</strong><br/><br/>Great characters, it goes from lowest of low of humanity to all the way up. FBI agent Mercy has a steel armor around her, but finally breaking down. If you read many books written by this author, you&apos;ll guess the ending.<br/>Plot is about one man trying to build militia group, paranoid, isolated and wary of government. Will keep you you reading.</span>
  <span id="freeText3899360781164996949" style="display:none"><strong>Good story,</strong><br /><br />Great characters, it goes from lowest of low of humanity to all the way up. FBI agent Mercy has a steel armor around her, but finally breaking down. If you read many books written by this author, you'll guess the ending.<br />Plot is about one man trying to build militia group, paranoid, isolated and wary of government. Will keep you you reading.</span>
