        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback 9781477848296" href="/book/show/33291346-a-merciful-truth">review of another edition</a>


          <div>
    <span class="greyText">Recommended to Linda  by: </span>
      <a href="/user/show/17889962-luli">Luli</a>
  </div>


          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/3919132-linda?shelf=dysfunctional-family">dysfunctional-family</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/3919132-linda?shelf=light-romance">light-romance</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/3919132-linda?shelf=multiple-povs">multiple-povs</a>, 
