  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/3394063554?book_show_action=true">Jun 20, 2020</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="CosmicDancer" class="user" itemprop="url" name="CosmicDancer" href="/user/show/4350198-cosmicdancer">CosmicDancer</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3394063554" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer2220370371015870113">Another winner from Kendra Elliot!<br/><br/>Loved this book, loved the suspense and the intrigue, and the undercurrent of romance between Truman and Mercy. Absolutely loved them!</span>

          </span>
        </div>


