  <span id="freeText4081154186813571972" style="display:none">This book picks up where the first book left off. Mercy Kilpatrick is an FBI and a "prepper" - survivalist awaiting for TEOFTWAWKI! Shunned by the males in her family, but prepared to win them back as long as it takes. Mercy teams up with Sheriff Truman (her love interest as well) to solve this murder mystery.<br /><br />A firebug is lose in Eagle's Nest, Oregon and the bug is also a murderer!<br /><br />Fairly fast paced and a good read over all. A few red herrings, twists and turns, and a surprise (at least to me, although something was tugging at me).<br /><br />4 solid stars and 2 thumbs up!</span>
